                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm not sure what is happening here but around 23 I started noticing that I would often take a quick hit when my tank would pull. I have a virtually flawless tank and never noticed this before 20. My assumption was that either his current initial aggro spell was graying out, or that it was some type of AI improvement / aggro change in harder mobs. I usually have the lowest ac in my group, so I can understand why the mob would try to take me out first. 
<br />

<br />
It reminds me of the current DPS thread in this forum. The dynamics of who in the group has what spells / abilities upgraded to what levels at their current level makes it really tough to determine anything without tons of evidence. If I played a tank for a while it would probably become clearer.
<br />

