                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Enchanter = Aggro, was for EQ1, same for EQ2 thank goodness we get reduce hate and aggro related spells.
<br />

<br />
Buffs in combat = aggro (usally more than damage spells).  So watch thoes group hastes.
<br />

<br />
As far as damage, Dots are less than DD's, I usally dont nuke till the mob is 80% or less.
<br />

<br />
Note:  With good tanks, aggro should be of little problem save for if you do group buffs in combat, they should be taunting.  Unfortunetly they do not always.  If you find yourself in a pick up group and your getting alot of aggro time to cast buffs less frequently and rely on dots heavily.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />______________________
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.teanobi.com" target="_blank" class="postlink">Japanese Tea</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
