                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It's already been answered, but just to add my 2cp -- any maintained spell will add to your hate. With chanters that can add up awful quick, if you have regular conc buffs, few breezes, group haste up that's a whole shedload of counters. If you cast a buff *on incoming* that's a sure fire way to get walloped!
<br />

<br />
In my experience any wandering kos that aggros will jump me or a druid first. On pulls the tank always socks out a taunt plus damage on inc (an arrow or whatever) and that does the trick fine.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal">Ilira [L65 Coercer] Cazic Thule[retired]
<br />
Ilira [L29 Coercer] Runnyeye </span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
